WEBVTT

00:12:29.262 --> 00:12:30.960
now, in addition to seeing,

00:12:30.984 --> 00:12:33.077
we're able to hear.

00:12:33.101 --> 00:12:36.648
This is a revolution in astronomy,

00:12:36.672 --> 00:12:40.240
like when Galileo invented the telescope.

00:12:40.859 --> 00:12:44.309
It's like when they added sound
to silent movies.

00:12:45.110 --> 00:12:47.836
This is just the beginning.

00:12:49.120 --> 00:12:51.012
We like to think

00:12:51.500 --> 00:12:57.767
that the road to science is very long --
very fun, but very long --

00:12:57.791 --> 00:13:04.154
and that we, this large,
international community of scientists,